        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛A卷一试",
        "question": "在△ABC中，$AB = 1$，$AC = 2$，$B - C = \\frac{2\\pi}{3}$，则△ABC的面积为______。",
        "solution": [
            "由正弦定理知 $\\frac{\\sin B}{\\sin C} = \\frac{AC}{AB} = 2$，又 $B - C = \\frac{2\\pi}{3}$，故",
            "$2\\sin C = \\sin B = \\sin(C + \\frac{2\\pi}{3}) = -\\frac{1}{2}\\sin C + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\cos C$",
            "即 $\\frac{5}{2}\\sin C = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\cos C$，所以 $\\tan C = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{5}$",
            "记△ABC的面积为 $S$。注意到 $A = \\pi - B - C = \\frac{\\pi}{3} - 2C$，故",
            "$S = \\frac{1}{2}AB \\cdot AC \\cdot \\sin A = \\sin A = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\cos 2C - \\frac{1}{2}\\sin 2C$",
            "由 $\\tan C = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{5}$ 知 $\\cos 2C = \\frac{1 - \\tan^{2}C}{1 + \\tan^{2}C} = \\frac{11}{14}$，$\\sin 2C = \\frac{2\\tan C}{1 + \\tan^{2}C} = \\frac{5\\sqrt{3}}{14}$",
            "从而 $S = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} \\cdot \\frac{11}{14} - \\frac{1}{2} \\cdot \\frac{5\\sqrt{3}}{14} = \\frac{3\\sqrt{3}}{14}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{3\\sqrt{3}}{14}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
