        "context": "2021年全国高中数学联合竞赛A卷解答题",
        "question": "已知复数列 $\\{z_{n}\\}$ 满足：$z_{1} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}$，$z_{n+1} = \\overline{z_{n}}(1 + z_{n}\\mathrm{i})$ ($n = 1,2,\\dots$)，其中i为虚数单位。求 $z_{2021}$ 的值。",
        "solution": [
            "对 $n \\in \\mathbb{N}^{*}$，设 $z_{n} = a_{n} + b_{n}\\mathrm{i}$ ($a_{n}, b_{n} \\in \\mathbb{R}$)，则",
            "$a_{n+1} + b_{n+1}\\mathrm{i} = z_{n+1} = \\overline{z_{n}}(1 + z_{n}\\mathrm{i}) = \\overline{z_{n}} + |z_{n}|^{2} \\cdot \\mathrm{i} = a_{n} - b_{n}\\mathrm{i} + (a_{n}^{2} + b_{n}^{2})\\mathrm{i}$",
            "因此 $a_{n+1} = a_{n}$，$b_{n+1} = a_{n}^{2} + b_{n}^{2} - b_{n}$",
            "又由 $z_{1} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}$ 知，$a_{1} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}, b_{1} = 0$，所以 $a_{n} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}$，进而",
            "$b_{n+1} = b_{n}^{2} - b_{n} + \\frac{3}{4}$",
            "即 $b_{n+1} - \\frac{1}{2} = b_{n}^{2} - b_{n} + \\frac{1}{4} = (b_{n} - \\frac{1}{2})^{2}$",
            "所以当 $n \\geq 2$ 时，$b_{n} = \\frac{1}{2} + (b_{1} - \\frac{1}{2})^{2^{n-1}} = \\frac{1}{2} + (-\\frac{1}{2})^{2^{n-1}} = \\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{1}{2^{2^{n-1}}}$",
            "于是 $z_{2021} = a_{2021} + b_{2021}\\mathrm{i} = \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} + (\\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{1}{2^{2^{2020}}})\\mathrm{i}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["$\\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2} + (\\frac{1}{2} + \\frac{1}{2^{2^{2020}}})\\mathrm{i}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
        "unit": null,
        "answer_type": "Expression",
        "error": null
    },
