        "question": "如图，正方体ABCD-EFGH的棱长为2，在正方形ABFE的内切圆上任取一点 $P_{1}$，在正方形BCGF的内切圆上任取一点 $P_{2}$，在正方形EFGH的内切圆上任取一点 $P_{3}$。求 $|P_{1}P_{2}| + |P_{2}P_{3}| + |P_{3}P_{1}|$ 的最小值与最大值。<img_14d3f509d9f7b50cefc3786f46fb64bdfc17efd909b49958534ee0241a074fb8>",
        "solution": [
            "以正方体的中心为原点，$\\overrightarrow{DA}$、$\\overrightarrow{DC}$、$\\overrightarrow{DH}$ 的方向分别为 $x$ 轴、$y$ 轴、$z$ 轴的正方向，建立空间直角坐标系",
            "根据条件，可设 $P_{1}(1, \\cos \\alpha_{1}, \\sin \\alpha_{1})$，$P_{2}(\\sin \\alpha_{2}, 1, \\cos \\alpha_{2})$，$P_{3}(\\cos \\alpha_{3}, \\sin \\alpha_{3}, 1)$",
            "约定 $P_{4} = P_{1}$，$\\alpha_{4} = \\alpha_{1}$。记 $d_{i} = |P_{i}P_{i+1}|$ ($i = 1,2,3$)，则",
            "$d_{i}^{2} = (1 - \\sin \\alpha_{i+1})^{2} + (1 - \\cos \\alpha_{i})^{2} + (\\sin \\alpha_{i} - \\cos \\alpha_{i+1})^{2}$",
            "记 $f = |P_{1}P_{2}| + |P_{2}P_{3}| + |P_{3}P_{1}|$",
            "先求 $f$ 的最小值。对 $i = 1,2,3$，根据上式与平均值不等式得",
            "$d_{i}^{2} \\geq (1 - \\sin \\alpha_{i+1})^{2} + (1 - \\cos \\alpha_{i})^{2} \\geq \\frac{1}{2}((1 - \\sin \\alpha_{i+1}) + (1 - \\cos \\alpha_{i}))^{2}$",
            "故 $d_{i} \\geq \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}(2 - \\sin \\alpha_{i+1} - \\cos \\alpha_{i})$。于是",
            "$f = d_{1} + d_{2} + d_{3} \\geq \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\sum_{i=1}^{3}(2 - \\sin \\alpha_{i+1} - \\cos \\alpha_{i}) = 3\\sqrt{2} - \\frac{\\sqrt{2}}{2}\\sum_{i=1}^{3}(\\sin \\alpha_{i} + \\cos \\alpha_{i})$",
            "$= 3\\sqrt{2} - \\sum_{i=1}^{3}\\sin(\\alpha_{i} + \\frac{\\pi}{4}) \\geq 3\\sqrt{2} - 3$",
            "当 $\\alpha_{i} = \\frac{\\pi}{4}$ ($i = 1,2,3$) 时，$f$ 可取到最小值 $3\\sqrt{2} - 3$",
            "再求 $f$ 的最大值。由前式知 $d_{i}^{2} = 4 - 2\\cos \\alpha_{i} - 2\\sin \\alpha_{i+1} - 2\\sin \\alpha_{i}\\cos \\alpha_{i+1}$",
            "注意到 $\\sin \\alpha_{i} \\geq -1$，$\\cos \\alpha_{i} \\geq -1$ ($i = 1,2,3$)，有",
            "$\\sum_{i=1}^{3}d_{i}^{2} = 12 - 2(\\sum_{i=1}^{3}\\sin \\alpha_{i+1} + \\sum_{i=1}^{3}\\cos \\alpha_{i} + \\sum_{i=1}^{3}\\sin \\alpha_{i}\\cos \\alpha_{i+1})$",
            "$= 18 - 2\\sum_{i=1}^{3}(1 + \\sin \\alpha_{i})(1 + \\cos \\alpha_{i+1}) \\leq 18$",
            "由柯西不等式知 $f^{2} \\leq 3(d_{1}^{2} + d_{2}^{2} + d_{3}^{2}) \\leq 54$，故 $f \\leq 3\\sqrt{6}$",
            "当 $\\alpha_{i} = \\pi$ ($i = 1,2,3$) 时，$f$ 可取到最大值 $3\\sqrt{6}$",
            "综上所述，$f$ 的最小值为 $3\\sqrt{2} - 3$，最大值为 $3\\sqrt{6}$"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["最小值：$3\\sqrt{2} - 3$，最大值：$3\\sqrt{6}$"],
        "is_multiple_answer": false,
