        "question": "给定正整数 $k$ ($k \\geq 2$) 与 $k$ 个非零实数 $a_{1}, a_{2}, \\dots, a_{k}$。证明：至多有有限个 $k$ 元正整数组 $(n_{1}, n_{2}, \\dots, n_{k})$，满足 $n_{1}, n_{2}, \\dots, n_{k}$ 互不相同，且 $a_{1} \\cdot n_{1}! + a_{2} \\cdot n_{2}! + \\dots + a_{k} \\cdot n_{k}! = 0$。",
        "solution": [
            "取定正整数 $N \\geq \\frac{|a_{1}| + |a_{2}| + \\cdots + |a_{k}|}{\\min_{1\\leq i\\leq k}|a_{i}|}$（注意 $a_{1}, a_{2}, \\dots, a_{k} \\neq 0$）",
            "我们证明，当正整数 $n_{1}, n_{2}, \\dots, n_{k}$ 满足条件时，必有 $\\max_{1\\leq i\\leq k}n_{i} \\leq N$",
            "假设不然，不妨设 $\\max_{1\\leq i\\leq k}n_{i} = n_{1} > N$。对 $i = 2, \\dots, k$，由于正整数 $n_{i} < n_{1}$，故",
            "$n_{i}! \\leq (n_{1} - 1)! = \\frac{n_{1}!}{n_{1}} < \\frac{n_{1}!}{N}$",
            "从而 $|a_{2} \\cdot n_{2}! + \\cdots + a_{k} \\cdot n_{k}!| \\leq \\sum_{i=2}^{k}|a_{i}| \\cdot n_{i}! < \\frac{n_{1}!}{N}\\sum_{i=2}^{k}|a_{i}| < \\frac{n_{1}!}{N}\\sum_{i=1}^{k}|a_{i}|$",
            "$\\leq \\min_{1\\leq i\\leq k}|a_{i}| \\cdot n_{1}! \\leq |a_{1}| \\cdot n_{1}!$",
            "但 $|a_{2} \\cdot n_{2}! + \\dots + a_{k} \\cdot n_{k}!| = |-a_{1} \\cdot n_{1}!| = |a_{1}| \\cdot n_{1}!$，矛盾",
            "所以，满足条件的正整数组 $(n_{1}, n_{2}, \\dots, n_{k})$ 至多有 $N^{k}$ 组。本题得证"
        ],
        "final_answer": ["见解析"],
